OL,3,CBig day or big decoy? Everything we
OL,4,Cknow about Taylor Swift's rumoured
OL,5,Cwedding
OL,7,FWords by Producer Lois Smith
OL,9,FThe US may not have a royal family,
OL,10,Fbut Taylor Swift's nuptials to fiance
OL,11,FTravis Kelce have been dubbed
OL,12,FAmerica's version of a royal wedding.
OL,14,FSpeculation from Swifties on the date,
OL,15,Fvenue, and guest list of one of the
OL,16,Fworld's wealthiest musicians has been
OL,17,Fbuilding from the moment the couple
OL,18,Fannounced their engagement in August
OL,19,Flast year.
OL,26,@rD@err
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
