OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1782915514
OL,3,CBig day or big decoy? Everything we
OL,4,Cknow about Taylor Swift's rumoured
OL,5,Cwedding
OL,7,FSwift is known for leaving easter eggs
OL,8,Fin the buildup to major career
OL,9,Fmoments, turning her fans into eagle-
OL,10,Feyed detectives, but the global pop
OL,11,Fsensation and her three-time NFL
OL,12,Fchampion fiance have stayed silent on
OL,13,Fthe details of their big day.
OL,15,FAlthough nothing has been confirmed by
OL,16,FSwift or Kelce's teams, the rumor mill
OL,17,Fis turning ` with perhaps some
OL,18,Fspeculation carrying credibility.
OL,20,FWhen and where is Swift rumoured to be
OL,21,Ftying the knot?
OL,26,@tD@Orr
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
