OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1782915514
OL,3,CBig day or big decoy? Everything we
OL,4,Cknow about Taylor Swift's rumoured
OL,5,Cwedding
OL,7,FThe star couple has not publicly said
OL,8,Fwhen they are getting married, but
OL,9,Freports largely suggest they could be
OL,10,Fset to tie the knot around July 4,
OL,11,Fwhich this year, will also mark the
OL,12,F250th US Independence Day.
OL,14,FSwift is known for hosting elaborate
OL,15,Fcelebrations to mark the American
OL,16,Fholiday, with her annual Fourth of
OL,17,FJuly party becoming an event in its
OL,18,Fown right, nicknamed "Taymerica" by
OL,19,Ffans.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1782915514
OL,3,CBig day or big decoy? Everything we
OL,4,Cknow about Taylor Swift's rumoured
OL,5,Cwedding
OL,7,FThis timing also fits with Kelce's
OL,8,Ffootball schedule, given the Kansas
OL,9,FCity Chiefs player once joked on his
OL,10,Fpodcast, New Heights, that he wouldn't
OL,11,Fmake friends "choose whether or not
OL,12,Fthey have to sell their tickets that
OL,13,Fweek".
OL,15,FAs the holiday nears, rumours that the
OL,16,Fcelebrity wedding of the year could
OL,17,Ftake place at Madison Square Garden
OL,18,F(MSG) in Midtown Manhattan have taken
OL,19,Fcentre stage.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
