PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1782915514
OL,3,CBig day or big decoy? Everything we
OL,4,Cknow about Taylor Swift's rumoured
OL,5,Cwedding
OL,7,FThe arena, referenced on Swift's Red
OL,8,Falbum, is normally a host venue for a
OL,9,Fvariety of sporting matches. But it
OL,10,Fhas also seen several global
OL,11,Fsuperstars perform - including Swift
OL,12,Fherself on eight different occasions.
OL,14,FUS President Donald Trump has also
OL,15,Fheld rallies at the 22,000 maximum
OL,16,Fcapacity arena.
OL,18,FPublic records show that the city
OL,19,Fissued a permit for loading and
OL,20,Funloading theatrical materials at the
OL,21,Farena from June 29 to July 4.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
