PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1782915514
OL,3,CBig day or big decoy? Everything we
OL,4,Cknow about Taylor Swift's rumoured
OL,5,Cwedding
OL,7,FMeanwhile, Winick Productions, a
OL,8,Fcompany that has produced red carpet
OL,9,Fevents for the Grammy and Tony award
OL,10,Fshows, also applied for a permit to
OL,11,Fset up a canopy or tent outside the
OL,12,FGarden for an event involving up to
OL,13,F999 people.
OL,15,FSeveral NFL players have reportedly
OL,16,Fbooked hotel rooms near the venue,
OL,17,Fwhich has underground VIP entrances
OL,18,Fand a level of privacy that is
OL,19,Fdifficult to achieve with an outdoor
OL,20,Fvenue.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
