OL,3,CBig day or big decoy? Everything we
OL,4,Cknow about Taylor Swift's rumoured
OL,5,Cwedding
OL,7,FWhilst not a traditional wedding venue
OL,8,Fchoice, it is available for private
OL,9,Frentals - advertising a banquet
OL,10,Fcapacity for 1,250 - and weddings have
OL,11,Fbeen hosted there before.
OL,13,FSly Stone got married to Kathy Silva
OL,14,Fat MSG in 1974, and more than 2,000
OL,15,Fcouples were also wed there in a
OL,16,Fcontroversial Unification Church mass
OL,17,Fceremony, officiated by the Rev. Sun
OL,18,FMyung Moon in 1982.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/14
