OL,3,CBig day or big decoy? Everything we
OL,4,Cknow about Taylor Swift's rumoured
OL,5,Cwedding
OL,7,FNew York City Mayor Zohran Mamdani
OL,8,Fjokingly referenced the reports of
OL,9,FSwift and Kelce's wedding taking place
OL,10,Fin the city during a press conference
OL,11,Flast month.
OL,13,FMamdani was answering questions about
OL,14,Fsafety during the World Cup when he
OL,15,Fsaid: "We know it coincides with July
OL,16,FFourth, America 250, Taylor Swift's
OL,17,Fwedding all happening at the same
OL,18,Ftime, and we are so excited to welcome
OL,19,Fthe world here."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
