OL,3,CBig day or big decoy? Everything we
OL,4,Cknow about Taylor Swift's rumoured
OL,5,Cwedding
OL,7,FBut could this be an elaborate red-
OL,8,Fherring?
OL,10,FDespite social media and tabloid
OL,11,Fspeculation, it is possible that the
OL,12,Fpreparations at MSG could be a decoy
OL,13,Fevent, or that Swift may have a
OL,14,Fsmaller ceremony followed by a larger
OL,15,Fparty at MSG.
OL,17,FSome fans online have said that MSG
OL,18,Fwould be too obvious a choice
OL,19,Faltogether, or that the duo's wish for
OL,20,Fprivacy around the wedding suggests a
OL,21,Fmore low-key affair.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
