OL,3,CBig day or big decoy? Everything we
OL,4,Cknow about Taylor Swift's rumoured
OL,5,Cwedding
OL,7,FSwift's 2025 engagement was a private
OL,8,Faffair in the garden of Kelce's 17,000-
OL,9,Fsquare-foot home.
OL,11,FMeanwhile, others on TikTok have
OL,12,Fthrown out wilder theories that the
OL,13,Fplanned event in New York could be an
OL,14,Falbum launch or a similar fan-based
OL,15,Fevent.
OL,17,FWho will make the star-studded guest
OL,18,Flist?
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
