OL,3,CBig day or big decoy? Everything we
OL,4,Cknow about Taylor Swift's rumoured
OL,5,Cwedding
OL,7,FSwift joked in October that "anyone
OL,8,FI've ever talked to" would be invited
OL,9,Fto the wedding, telling Graham Norton
OL,10,Fthat she believed "the only stressful
OL,11,Fweddings" are those that are small and
OL,12,Fforce people to make aggressive cuts
OL,13,Fto the guest list".
OL,15,FWho exactly has received an invite
OL,16,Fremains shrouded in secrecy, but it is
OL,17,Fhighly likely there will be a host of
OL,18,FA-listers in attendance.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
