OL,3,CBig day or big decoy? Everything we
OL,4,Cknow about Taylor Swift's rumoured
OL,5,Cwedding
OL,7,FFor Swift, celebrity friends Selena
OL,8,FGomez, the Haim sisters, Emma Stone,
OL,9,Fand Gigi Hadid are likely to be there
OL,10,Fcelebrating, as well as childhood best
OL,11,Ffriend Abigail Anderson Berard, who
OL,12,Fhas been in several music videos
OL,13,Fthroughout the years.
OL,15,FEd Sheeran has been all but confirmed
OL,16,Fas a guest, with Swift hinting in
OL,17,Fprevious interviews that the Halifax-
OL,18,Fborn singer-songwriter could even
OL,19,Fperform.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
