OL,3,CBig day or big decoy? Everything we
OL,4,Cknow about Taylor Swift's rumoured
OL,5,Cwedding
OL,7,FAside from family, Kelce's Kansas City
OL,8,FChiefs teammate Patrick Mahomes and
OL,9,Fhis wife, Brittany Mahomes, will also
OL,10,Flikely be there.
OL,12,FChiefs coach Andy Reid said he
OL,13,Fcouldn't talk about it when asked if
OL,14,Fhe was going to the wedding.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G13/14
