OL,3,CBig day or big decoy? Everything we
OL,4,Cknow about Taylor Swift's rumoured
OL,5,Cwedding
OL,7,F"If it's like when I got married, my
OL,8,Fwife did everything, so I just kind of
OL,9,Ffollowed her lead on it, showed up,
OL,10,Fright? Maybe he's doing more, but he
OL,11,Flooks like he's pretty focused on this
OL,12,Fjob here, too," Reid said in early
OL,13,FJune.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G14/14
